name: Dina Abdel
text: Pizza hut not my favorite place to go to eat pizza, but they have good pizza. They have good service and very nice employees. The parking lot and the restaurant is small. The only thing is that they need to clean the floors good.

name: Haroon Tanveer
text: The only relatively good aspect was the pizza. Service was terrible. The restaurant was empty, however it took over an hour for the pizza to get made. Many of the tables were dirty and the place did not have a welcoming feel to it.

name: Aung Tin
text: I love pizza to order by phone but I feel upset with the customer service because of my English  accent they don't wnat to serve me. I will tell all my friends not to order pizza from Pizza Hut if your English accent is not good enough.

name: Malic Selimi
text: When I'm hungry they feed me
